OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FMostly dry
OL,6,Fthis evening with some late sunshine.
OL,7,FThen the rest of the night will be
OL,8,Flargely dry with clear periods and the
OL,9,Fodd passing shower. Fresh
OL,10,Fsouthwesterly winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FA dry day with with variable
OL,13,Famounts of cloud some sunny intervals.
OL,14,FFresh southwesterly winds across
OL,15,FShetland at first.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FMostly
OL,18,Fdry on Monday, perhaps some low cloud
OL,19,Fand rain later. Generally dry although
OL,20,Fmostly cloudy on Tuesday and Wednesday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
